---
title: Speedy Sausage 'Ziti' with Fresh Penne and Balsamic Spinach Salad
description: We've swapped regular pasta for fresh to cut down your cooking time and deliver slow-cooked flavour in a flash. Rich Italian sausage and a hearty tomato sauce bubble and broil together under a blanket of creamy ricotta and melty mozzarella.
